reviewText: I was happy to find silent movies starring Hoot Gibson.

I bought this set as a gift, so this is something of a review by proxy.  My brother, to whom I gave these DVDs, and who is a great fan of old westerns and has hundreds of videos of vintage shows, loved this set.  He said that some of the episodes in this set were things that he had been searching for unsuccessfully for years.  So I can at least say that one hard-core western lover found this to be a good collection.
